{"tid":2290394,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"王敏德戴「黃圈」口罩， 遭藍絲狙擊後急刪文","createTime":"2020-11-18T03:29:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T03:35:59.000Z","uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"42f6b973a9aa0a70cd6052de4299bffd34bda6c0","tid":2290394,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:29:41.000Z","msg":"可是，王敏德雖然經常演警察，但和大部份藝人一樣，自去年社會運動開始，他除了在IG貼上到郊外攝影或駕駛直升機的照片外，大部份時間都是享受人生和家庭樂，甚少在政治議題上表達立場。而他昨日亦如常貼出和太太馬詩慧拍拖到跑馬地一餐廳食晏的照片。可是，照片一post，卻引來藍絲網民狙擊。事緣照片中，他戴上一個印有「F.D.N.O.L.」的黃色口罩，有指「F.D.N.O.L.」是港人訴求的縮寫，因此有網民就留言「以後不要再找他扮飛虎，影衰警察！」更有網民直指他一家人擁有美籍護照。受到網民一輪攻擊後，王敏德即時將帖文刪除。<br />\n<br />\n其實王敏德所戴印有「F.D.N.O.L.」的黃色口罩，是出自店舖「黃廠」Yellow Factory <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201117/LAMTSSKCXBE7RBAB7GFR6C4BEY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201117%2FLAMTSSKCXBE7RBAB7GFR6C4BEY%2F&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1fo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=fd5512eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201117%2FLAMTSSKCXBE7RBAB7GFR6C4BEY%2F&h=ae85f0fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201117/LAMTSSKCXBE7RBAB7GFR6C4BEY/</a>"},{"pid":"af5a5232b5fd0ba749c756d8d39619d4f9fe8374","tid":2290394,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:30:04.000Z","msg":"藍衛兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00bd90d586ecdd97b7156f2dbf441d168d7bd833","tid":2290394,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:30:22.000Z","msg":"Blue nazi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca39334a005afa2fc47bf06c2f8983681c90403","tid":2290394,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c7fe447a1915aaa0be3d3c060